description: List all field-level encryption configurations that have been created in CloudFront for this account.

nested_items.name: FieldLevelEncryptionList
nested_items.description: Returns a list of all field-level encryption configurations that have been created in CloudFront for this account.

nested_items.name: NextMarker
nested_items.description: If there are more elements to be listed, this element is present and contains the value that you can use for the Marker request parameter to continue listing your configurations where you left off.

nested_items.name: MaxItems
nested_items.description: The maximum number of elements you want in the response body.

nested_items.name: Quantity
nested_items.description: The number of field-level encryption items.

nested_items.name: Items
nested_items.description: An array of field-level encryption items.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The unique ID of a field-level encryption item.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The last time that the summary of field-level encryption items was modified.

nested_items.name: Comment
nested_items.description: An optional comment about the field-level encryption item. The comment cannot be longer than 128 characters.

nested_items.name: QueryArgProfileConfig
nested_items.description: A summary of a query argument-profile mapping.

nested_items.name: ForwardWhenQueryArgProfileIsUnknown
nested_items.description: Flag to set if you want a request to be forwarded to the origin even if the profile specified by the field-level encryption query argument, fle-profile, is unknown.

nested_items.name: QueryArgProfiles
nested_items.description: Profiles specified for query argument-profile mapping for field-level encryption.

nested_items.description: Number of profiles for query argument-profile mapping for field-level encryption.

nested_items.name: Items
nested_items.description: Number of items for query argument-profile mapping for field-level encryption.

nested_items.name: QueryArg
nested_items.description: Query argument for field-level encryption query argument-profile mapping.

nested_items.name: ProfileId
nested_items.description: ID of profile to use for field-level encryption query argument-profile mapping.

nested_items.name: ContentTypeProfileConfig
nested_items.description: A summary of a content type-profile mapping.

nested_items.name: ForwardWhenContentTypeIsUnknown
nested_items.description: The setting in a field-level encryption content type-profile mapping that specifies what to do when an unknown content type is provided for the profile. If true, content is forwarded without being encrypted when the content type is unknown. If false (the default), an error is returned when the content type is unknown.
